snippet: Scott Sharp celebrated a second win at the Rolex 24 at Daytona Beach, Fla., 20 years after his first victory, in a race in which most of the top contenders fell apart.
abstract: Scott Sharp wins Rolex 24 auto race at Daytona Beach, Fla.
